{"tid":2178811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《香港01》鼓勵員工參與自願檢測 員工憂不檢測會留下紀錄","createTime":"2020-08-28T15:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T16:41:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c8788316a7f1ee4eec9d1d9571e220c26a02690","tid":2178811,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/2M2MS2PPBJHX3LXG76ASOIO3ZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2F2M2MS2PPBJHX3LXG76ASOIO3ZM%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=488f0c75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2F2M2MS2PPBJHX3LXG76ASOIO3ZM%2F&h=b8eca4ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/2M2MS2PPBJHX3LXG76ASOIO3ZM/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾多次在觀點文章欄目撰文支持「全民檢測」的《香港01》，今日（28日）向員工發通告，指支持政府推出的「普及社區檢測計劃」，故鼓勵同事參與，並容許同事在毋須申放任何假期的情況下進行檢測，可在完成檢測後將結果交予公司，該工作日可領全薪。有員工憂心此舉變相記錄員工是否有進行檢測，但亦有編採部員工稱，沒有收到任何指示要求員工必須進行檢測。"},{"pid":"04d700b7062c60bd9a58d348befce9272dfcbfc5","tid":2178811,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"投名狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[重開] 精英SS級 國際戰線：&ldquo;Letters to the Editor&rdquo; 歡迎你！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2178434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2178434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33f9f90946adae20615cf0dd1c635f3d29c2d9e4","tid":2178811,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:00:35.000Z","msg":"日薪&gt;500<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另類利益輸送/賄賂<br />\nICAC<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"